attributes.action: Lift ban on import of rescue animals from Romania, Ukraine, Belarus and Poland
attributes.additional_details: The government has stopped anyone from rescuing animals from these countries and adopting them here. These animals need our help and there is surely no reason that with checks in place that they cannot be rehomed safely in the UK. Please lift the ban!
attributes.background: The Government should lift the suspension on rescuing animals from these countries if they meet the standard entry requirements including vaccinations and checks.
